title: Oh Captain, my Captain (Marvel)
body:
Oh Captain, my Captain (Marvel)

It’s been a long road, but Marvel finally debuted the first female-led superhero film in a 21-film franchise. And while I wish that the movie they had delivered was just a bit better, it’s still a fun space romp and confirms what has been true all along: That women really were meant to rule the galaxies.

I think there’s a misconception that if you’re a woman who enjoys seeing female-led films…

blog.title: Once Upon a Custom Funko
blog.description: A side blog for my Once Upon a Time custom funkos.  I do take commissions to replicate ones I have already done ONLY.  Please message me to talk about commissions or visit my etsy shop at https://www.etsy.com/shop/OnceUponaCustom

summary: Captain Carol Danvers Captain Marvel Air Force Uniform Custom Funko Carol in her dress uniform with MCU hair.  I will be doing a...
caption:
Captain Carol Danvers Captain Marvel Air Force Uniform Custom Funko

Carol in her dress uniform with MCU hair.  I will be doing a version with the short comic hair as well.  I do want to point out that having looked through lots of pictures of Carol in uniform no one drawing that comic seems to have ever bothered to look up what a woman’s air force uniform looks like.  The hair isn’t quite right on the head I’ve used but it’s the closest match to the MCU one I could get (there aren’t enough funko heads with buns).  I’ve otherwise given her what would have been approriate for a mid 1990s air force captain.  Her body is Selina Meyers from Veep and her head is the Tower Recon Specialist from Fortnite.

Under the cut you will find some of the ways Marvel artists have done air force dress uniforms on Carol…

I will take commissions to replicate this funko, please contact privately to discuss price as the market for the figures in which I make these out of can change wildly.  Ask me about my etsy shop.

The wrong color.  Wearing no insignia.  Wearing hat inside.  Hair loose and long.

Hair loose and long.  Odd insignia.  Wearing a man’s uniform.

Wearing a man’s uniform.  Wearing patches which the air force doesn’t do.

summary: i know i’m  a little late but i just saw captain marvel, and i’m sure there are a million different posts outlining all the...
body: i know i’m  a little late but i just saw captain marvel, and i’m sure there are a million different posts outlining all the awesome things about this movie (and there were a lot of awesome things) but can i just say i was SO GLAD when space jude law was baiting her to fight mano-a-mano and she just pulled an indiana jones on him, because if any super dude would have been in that scenario they would have gotten their pride hurt and just gone into the most pointless fight ever. meanwhile carol is like ”lazerhands!” and yeeted him into a big rock.
